    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2005 BMW M3 represents the pinnacle of the E46 chassis, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. Meticulously preserved, this example features a factory-reinforced rear subframe and proactive rod bearing replacement, addressing the platform's critical mechanical requirements. Power is delivered via a longitudinal Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains strictly factory-spec with zero bushing deflection, ensuring the telepathic turn-in and lateral stability synonymous with the M-division. Every VIN tag is present, the paint depth is uniform across all panels, and the Nappa leather interior retains its original matte finish. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
